title: Karin's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Catering, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small organic food menu featuring dishes inspired from around the world. Supports the slow food movement and caters to gluten free and special diets upon request. Vegetarian and vegan starters and mains. Hosts cooking demos and events.
